      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "In response to an appeal issued\nby Mayor futile of Fernie for\nmore help the chamber of com\nmerce will meet tomorrow noon to\ntake up the question of further re-\nlief for the fire stricken city. Mayor\nfutile says money is needed to en-\nable sufferers to erect shelter be-\nfore cold fall weather comes and\ntot provide bedding and necessities.\nBut $50 OF 5000 saved their house\nhold belongings.\n\n\nThe chamber of commerce ex.\npoets to issue general relief call\nand looks to the city to respond &c\nthe best of its ability, w, d. Fin\nley, who had charge of the Spo-\nkane relief. will make a full re-\nport at tomorrow meeting."
    }
  ]
